PersonalMission.Name: LT-6: Battle Support
PersonalMission.Description: Damage caused with your assistance is one of the most important statistics for light tanks. If this statistic is high, that means you were an asset to your team in battle.
PersonalMission.Hint: The longer your view range, the better. Try to spot enemy vehicles and hit their tracks while keeping yourself alive. Equipment such as Coated Optics and Binocular Telescope can help you to spot the enemy from a safe distance.

Primary.Conditions: •  Enable your allies to cause damage to 6 vehicles by spotting them or destroying their tracks

Secondary.Conditions: •  Enable your allies to destroy 3 vehicles by spotting them or destroying their tracks
